Project Summary
===============
Supabase Counter — een interactieve teller waarvan elke actie (increment, decrement, reset) als log wordt weggeschreven naar Supabase. Bij laden wordt de laatste opgeslagen waarde opgehaald. Gebouwd op Next.js 15 / Tailwind CSS 4 / Supabase JS v2.

Architecture Overview
====================
Single-page Next.js App Router app. Server Components by default; any interactivity lives in client components under `components/`. Top-level routing files (`page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `not-found.tsx`, `error.tsx`, `loading.tsx`) are all server components — `'use client'` NEVER appears at this level (breaks WebContainer prerendering). Styling is Tailwind CSS 4 via `@import "tailwindcss";` in `app/globals.css`.

Key Components
==============

- **Page** (`app/page.tsx`) — Server Component wrapper. Renders `<Counter />`.
- **Counter** (`components/Counter.tsx`) — Client Component. Beheert `count`, `loading`, `saving` en `logs` state. Haalt bij mount de laatste `count_value` op uit Supabase; schrijft bij elke klik een nieuw log-record. Toont de laatste 5 acties onder de teller.
- **Supabase client** (`lib/supabase.ts`) — Typed Supabase client via `@supabase/supabase-js`, geladen met `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` en `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`.
- **Database types** (`types/database.ts`) — TypeScript type definitions voor de `counter_logs` tabel.
- **RootLayout** (`app/layout.tsx`) — Root HTML shell. Loads Geist Sans + Geist Mono via `next/font/google` and defines SEO metadata. Antialiasing enabled.
- **Error Boundary** (`app/error.tsx`) — Runtime error recovery with retry.
- **NotFound** (`app/not-found.tsx`) — 404 page. Plain server component using only `Link` from `next/link` and inline SVG.
- **Loading** (`app/loading.tsx`) — Route transition spinner.

Invariants
==========
- `app/*/page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `not-found.tsx`, `error.tsx` are ALWAYS Server Components. No `'use client'`, no hooks, no event handlers at this layer.
- Client interactivity (useState, useEffect, onClick) lives in `components/*.tsx` with `'use client'`.
- Supabase project: `jlzdlrxjdlhauomfomro`. Tabel: `counter_logs` (id uuid, action text, count_value integer, created_at timestamptz). RLS aan, anon mag insert én select.
- Env vars: `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` en `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` in `.env.local`.
- Elke klik insert een nieuw record; de teller-waarde wordt afgeleid van het meest recente record (geen UPDATE, alleen INSERT).
- Bij lege tabel (`PGRST116` error) start de teller op 0.
- `.env.local` exists at project root but is managed by the app (not written by agents directly).

Notes for agents
================
- Dependencies, versions, and the directory tree are NOT duplicated here. Read `package.json` or `list_directory` for that.
- When you change the project structure, update THIS file accordingly: add new components under Key Components, document new invariants, update the Architecture Overview if the fundamental shape shifts.
